hadiths[51]{hadithnumber,text}:
8,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Islam ki buniyad panch chizon par qaaim ki gaee hai. awwal gawahi dena ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur beshak Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke sachey rasool hain aur Namaz qaaim karna aur zakat ada karna aur Haj karna aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhna.
9,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke eman ki sath (60) se kuchh uper shakhein hain. aur haya (sharm) bhi eman ki aik shaakh hai.
10,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya musalman wo hai jiski zaban aur hath se musalman mehfooz rahen aur muhajir wo hai jawan kaamon ko chhod de jin se Allah ne mana farmaya, abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (rh)) ne farmaya aur abu-Muawia ne ham ko hadis bayan ki Daawood-bin-abii-Hind ne, unhon-ne riwayat ki Aamir Shabi se, unhon-ne kaha ke maine suna Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas se, wo hadis bayan kartey hain janab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( wahi mazkura (uper zikr) hadis) aur kaha ke Abdul-Aala ne riwayat kya Dawud se, unhon-ne Aamir se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
11,logon ne puchha ya Rasulullah ! kon sa Islam afzal hai? to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya wo jiske manney waley musalmanon ki zaban aur hath se sarey musalman salamati mein rahen.
12,"aik din aik aadmi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kon sa Islam behtar hai? farmaya ke tum khana khilao, aur jis ko pehchano usko bhi aur jisko na pehchano usko bhi, gharaz ye ki sab ko salam karo."
13,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum mein se koi shakhs emaandaar na hoga jab tak apne bhai ke liye wo na chahey jo apne-aapke ke liye chahta hai.
14,"beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, qism hai us zaat ki jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. tum mein se koi bhi emaandaar na hoga jab tak mein uske walid aur aulad se bhi zyada uska mahboob na bin jaun."
15,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum mein se koi shakhs emaandaar na hoga jab tak uske walid aur uski aulad aur tamam logon se zyada uske dil mein meri mohabbat na ho jaey.
16,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya teen khaslatein aisi hain ke jis mein ye paida ho jayen usne eman ki mithas ko pa liya. awwal ye ke Allah aur uska rasool uske nazdeek sabse zyada mahboob bin jaaein, doosrey ye ke wo kisi insan se mahz Allah ki raza ke liye mohabbat rakhe. teesrey ye ke wo kufr mein wapas lotney ko aisa bura janey jaisa ke aag mein daley janey ko bura janta hai."
17,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Ansar se mohabbat rakhna eman ki nishani hai aur Ansar se keena rakhna nifaq ki nishani hai.
18,"Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) jo badr ki ladai mein Sharik they aur Lailatal-Aqbaa ke (12) naqeebon mein se they. farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt jab aap ke gird sahaba ki aik jamat baithi hui thi farmaya ke mujh se bait karo is baat par ke Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na karogey, chori na karogey, zina na karogey, apni aulad ko qatl na karogey aur na jan-boojhkar kisi par koi nahaq bohtan bandhogey aur kisi bhi achi baat mein (Allah ki) nafarmani na karogey. jo koi tum mein (is ahad ko) pura karega to uska sawab Allah ke zimmey hai aur jo koi un ( buri baton ( mein se kisi ko bhi karey aur usey duniya main (Islami qanoon ke tehet) saza de di gaee to ye saza uske ( gunahon ke) liye badla ho jaeygi aur jo koi unmein se kisi baat mein mubtala ho gaya aur Allah ne uske ( gunah ( ko chipa liya to phir uska ( mamla ( Allah ke hawale hai, agar chahey maaf karey aur agar chahey saza de-dey. (Ubada kehtey hain ke) phir ham sab ne un (sab baton ( par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait kar li."
19,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya wo waqt qareeb hai jab musalman ka (sab se) umda maal (uiski bakriyan hongi). jinke peechhey wo pahadon ki chotiyon aur barsati wadiyon main apne Deen ko bachaney ke liye bhag jaeyga
20,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ko kisi kaam ka hukm detey to wo aisa hi kaam hota jiske karne ki logon mein taqat hoti (is par) sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! ham log to aap jaisey nahi hain (aap to masoom hain) aur aap ki Allah paak ne agli pichhli sab khataein maaf farma di hain. (is liye hamein apne se kuchh zyada ibadat karne ka hukm farmaiye) (ye sun kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) naraz huey yahan tak ke narazgi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehre Mubarak se zahir honey lagi phir farmaya ke beshak main tum sabse zyada Allah se darta hun aur tum sabse zyada usey janta hun. ( to tum mujh se badh kar ibadat nahi kar saktey ( .
21,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jis shakhs mein ye teen baatein hongi wo eman ka maza pa lega, aik ye ke wo shakhs jisey Allah aur uska rasool unke maa-siwa se zyada azeez hon aur doosrey ye ke jo kisi bandey se mahz Allah hi ke liye mohabbat karey aur teesri baat ye ke jisey Allah ne kufr se nijat di ho, phir dobara kufr ikhtiyar karne ko wo aisa bura samjhey jaisa aag mein gir janey ko bura janta hai."
22,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab jannati jannat main aur dozakhi dozakh mein dakhil ho jaengey. Allah paak farmaeyga, jiske dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar ( bhi) eman ho, usko bhi dozakh se nikaal lo. tab ( aisey log ( dozakh se nikaal liye jaeinge aur wo jal kar koiley ki tarah siyah ho chukey hongey. phir zindagi ki nehar mein ya barish ke pani mein daley jaengey. ( yahan rawi ko shak ho gaya hai ke uper ke rawi ne kon sa lafz istemal kya (us waqt wo daney ki tarah ug aaeingey jis tarah nadi ke kinarey daney ug aatey hain. kya tum ne nahi dekha ke daana zardi maail pech dar pech nikalta hai. Wuhaib ne kaha ke ham se Amr ne ( حياء ( ki bajaey) ( حياة ( , Mina aur (خردل من ايمان ) ki bajaey (خردل من خير) ka lafz bayan kya."
23,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aik waqt so raha tha, maine khuwab mein dekha ke log mere samney pesh kiye ja rahe hain aur wo kurtey pahney huey hain. kisi ka kurta seeney tak hai aur kisi ka us se neecha hai. (phir) mere samney Umar-bin-Khattab laey gaey. un (ke badan ( par (jo ( kurtaa tha. usey wo ghaseet rahe they. (yani unka kurta zameen tak neecha tha) sahaba ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah! iski kya tabeer hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (is se) Deen murad hai."
24,aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik Ansari shakhs ke paas se guzrey is haal mein ke wo apne aik bhai se keh rahe they ke tum itni sharm kyon kartey ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us Ansari se farmaya ke usko uske haal par rehney do kyonke haya bhi eman hi ka aik hissey hai.
25,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, mujhey (Allah ki taraf se) hukm diya gaya hai ke logon se jang karun us waqt tak ke wo is baat ka iqrar kar lein ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi hai aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke sachey rasool hain aur Namaz ada karne lagein aur zakat dein, jis waqt wo ye karne lagengey to mujh se apne jaan w maal ko mehfooz kar lengey, siwaey Islam ke haq ke. (raha unke dil ka haal to) unka hisab Allah ke zimme hai."
26,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum kya gaya ke kon sa amal sabse afzal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah aur uske rasool par eman lana'' kaha gaya, iske baad kon sa? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ''Allah ki raah mein jihad karna'' kaha gaya, phir kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''hajje-mabroor''."
27,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand logon ko kuchh Atiya diya aur Sad wahan maujood they. (wo kehtey hain ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein se aik shakhs ko kuchh na diya. halanke wo unmein mujhey sabse zyada pasand tha. maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne falan ko kuchh na diya halanke main usey momin guman karta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya momin ya musalman? main thodi der chup reh kar phir pehli baat dohraney laga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi dobara wahi jawab diya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Sad! bawajud ye ke aik shakhs mujhey zyada azeez hai (phir bhi mein usey nazar andaz karke) kisi aur doosrey ko us khof ki wjah se ye maal de deta hun ke (wo apni kamzori ki wjah se Islam se phir jaey aur) Allah usey aag mein aundha daal de. is hadis ko Younus, Saleh Mamar aur Zohri ke bhatije Abdullah ne Zohri se riwayat kya."
28,aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha kon sa Islam behtar hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke too khana khilaey aur har shakhs ko salam karey chahe usko to janta ho ya na janta ho.
29,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mujhey dozakh dikhlai gaee to usmein zyada tar auratein thin jo kufr karti hain. kaha gaya ya Rasulullah ! kya wo Allah ke sath kufr karti hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khawind ki na-shukri karti hain. aur ehsan ki na-shukri karti hain. agar tum umr bhar unmein se kisi ke sath ehsan kartey raho. phir tumhari taraf se kabhi koi unke khayal mein na-gawari ki baat ho jaey to fauran keh uthegi ke maine kabhi bhi tujh se koi bhalai nahi dekhi.
30,"main us shakhs (Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ki madad karne ko chalaa. rastey mein mujhko Abu-Bakra mile. puchha kahan jaate ho? maine kaha, us shakhs (Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ki madad karne ko jata hun. Abu-Bakra ne kaha apne ghar ko lot jao. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they jab 2 musalman apni-apni talwarein lekar bhid jayen to qaatil aur maqtool donon dozakhi hain. maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! qaatil to khair (zaroor dozakhi hona chaahiye) maqtool kyon? farmaya ''wo bhi apne sathi ko mar dalney ki hirs rakhta tha.'' (mauqa paata to wo usey zaroor qatl kar deta dil ke pakke irade par wo dozakhi hua)."
31,main Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se Rabza mein mila wo aik joda pahney huey they aur unka ghulam bhi joda pahney huey tha. maine uski wajah malum ki to kehney lagey ke maine aik shakhs yani ghulam ko bura-bhala kaha tha aur uski maa ki ghairat dilai (yani gali di) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye malum karke mujh se farmaya aey Abu-Zar ! to ne usey maa ke naam se ghairat dilai beshak tujh mein abhi kuchh zamana jahiliyat ka asar baqi hai. ( yad rakho ( ma-tehet log tumharey bhai hain. Allah ne (apni kisi maslihat ki bina par) unhein tumharey qabzey mein de rakha hai to jiske ma-tehet uska koi bhai ho to usko bhi wahi khilaey jo aap khata hai aur wahi kapda usey pehnaey jo aap pehnta hai aur unko itney kaam ki takleef na do ke unke liye mushkil ho jaey aur agar koi sakht kaam dalo to tum khud bhi unki madad karo.
32,jab sura Al-Anaam ki ye aayat utri jo log eman laey aur unhon-ne apne eman mein gunahon ki aamezish (milawat) nahi ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! ye to bahut hi mushkil hai. ham mein kon aisa hai jisne gunah nahi kya. tab Allah paak ne sura luqman ki ye aayat utari ( إن الشرك لظلم عظيم‏ (ke beshak shirk bada zulm hai.
33,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, munafiq ki alamatein teen hain. jab baat karey jhoot boley, jab wada karey iske khilaf karey aur jab usko ameen banaya jaey to khayanat kare."
34,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke char aadatein jis kisi mein hon to wo khalis munafiq hai aur jis kisi mein un charon mein se aik aadat ho to wo ( bhi) nifaq hi hai, jab tak usey na chhod de. (wo ye hain) jab usey ameen banaya jaey to ( amanat mein) khayanat karey aur baat kartey waqt jhoot boley aur jab ( kisi se) ahad karey to usey pura na karey aur jab ( kisi se) ladey to gaaliyon par utar aaey. us hadis ko Shoba ne ( bhi) Sufiyan ke sath Aamash se riwayat kya hai."
35,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jo shakhs shabe-qadr eman ke sath mahz sawabe-aakhirat ke liye zikr w ibadat mein guzaarey, uske pichhle gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain."
36,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein (jihad ke liye) nikla , Allah uska zaamin ho gaya. ( Allah Taala farmata hai) usko meri zaat par yaqin aur mere paighambaron ki tasdeeq ne (is sarfaroshi ke liye ghar se) nikala hai. (main is baat ka zaamin hon (ke ya to usko wapas kar dun sawab aur maale-ghanimat ke saath, ya ( Shahid honey ke baad) jannat mein dakhil kar dun ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (aur agar main apni ummat par (is kaam ko) dushwar na samajhta to lashkar ka sath na chhorta aur meri khahish hai ke Allah ki raah mein maara jaun, phir zinda kya jaun, phir maara jaun, phir zinda kya jaun, phir maara jaun."
37,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo koi Ramazan mein (raaton ko) eman rakh kar aur sawab ke liye ibadat karey uske agley gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain.
38,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne Ramazan ke rozey eman aur khalis niyat ke sath rakhey uske pichhley gunah bakhsh diye gaey.
39,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya beshak Deen aasan hai aur jo shakhs Deen mein sakhti ikhtiyar karega to Deen is par ghalib aa jaeyga (aur uski sakhti na chal sakegi) to (is liye) apne amal mein pukhtagi ikhtiyar karo aur jahan tak mumkin ho miyaanaa rawii barto aur khush ho jao (ke us tarze-amal se tum ko darain ke faayede hasil hongey) aur subah aur do-pahar aur Sham aur kisi qadr raat main ( ibadat se) madad hasil karo. (panch waqt ki Namaz bhi murad ho sakti hai ke pabandi se ada karo.)
40,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Madina tashrif laey to pahley apni nanihal mein utrey , jo Ansar they. aur wahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sola ya satrah maah baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khahish thi ke aap ka qibla Baitullah ki taraf ho (jab Baitullah ki taraf Namaz padhney ka hukm ho gaya) to sabse pehli Namaz jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ki taraf padhi Asr ki Namaz thi. wahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath logon ne bhi Namaz padhi, phir aap ke sath Namaz padhney walon mein se aik aadmi nikla aur uska masjid (bani-Harisa) ki taraf guzar hua to wo log rukoo mein they. wo bola ke main Allah ki gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhi hai. (ye sun kar) wo log usi haalat mein Baitullah ki taraf ghoom gaey aur jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke Namaz padha kartey they, yahood aur Esai khush hotey they magar jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ki taraf munh pher liya to unhein ye baat na-gawar hui. Zuhair (eik rawi ( kehtey hain ke ham se Abu-Ishaq ne Bara se ye hadis bhi naql ki hai ke qible ki tabdili se pahley kuchh musalman intiqal kar chuke they. to hamein ye malum na ho saka ke unki namazon ke barey mein kya kahein. tab Allah ne ye aayat nazil ki ( وما كان الله ليضيع إيمانكم) ( al-Baqara: 143 ( ."
41,unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye irshad farmatey huey suna ke jab (eik ( banda musalman ho jaey aur uska Islam umda ho ( yaqin w Khuloos ke sath ho) to Allah uske gunah ko jo usney us (Islam laaney) se pahley kya maaf farma deta hai aur ab iske baad ke liye badla shuru ho jata hai (yaani) aik neki ke badle das guna se lekar saat so guna tak (sawab (aur aik burai ka usi burai ke mutabiq (badla diya jata hai) magar ye ke Allah Taala us burai se bhi darguzar kare. (aur usey bhi maaf farma de. ye bhi uske liye aasan hai.)
42,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se koi shakhs jab apne Islam ko umda bana ley (yani nifaq aur dikhawey se paak kar ley) to har nek kaam jo wo karta hai uske badle das se lekar saat so guna tak nekiyan likhi jati hain aur har bura kaam jo karta hai to wo utna hi likha jata hai (jitna ke usne kya hai).
43,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (eik din) unke paas aaey, us waqt aik aurat mere paas baithi thi, aap ne malum kya ye kon hai? maine arz kya, falan aurat aur uski Namaz (ke ishtiyaaq aur pabandi) ka zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya thehar jao (sun lo ke) tum par itna hi amal wajib hai jitney amal ki tumharey andar taqat hai. Allah ki qasam! (sawab dene se) Allah nahi uktata, magar tum (amal kartey kartey ( uktaa jaogey aur Allah ko Deen (ka ( wahi amal zyada pasand hai jiski hamesha pabandi ki ja sakey. (aur insan baghair uktaey usey anjam de) ."
44,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jis shakhs ne ( لا إله إلا الله ( keh liya aur uske dil mein jau barabar bhi (emaan) hai to wo (eik na aik din) dozakh se zaroor niklega aur dozakh se wo shakhs ( bhi) zaroor niklega jisne kalima padha aur uske dil mein gehun ke daane ke barabar khair hai aur dozakh se wo ( bhi) niklega jisne kalima padha aur uske dil mein aik zarra barabar bhi khair hai. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (rh)) farmatey hain ke Aban ne b-riwayat Qatada b-waaste Anas (Raziallahu anhu) rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( khair ( ki jagah ( eimaan (ka lafz naql kya hai.
45,aik Yahudi ne unse kaha ke aey ameerul-momineen ! tumhari kitab ( Quran ( mein aik aayat hai jisey tum padhtey ho. agar wo ham yahudiyon par nazil hoti to ham us (ke nuzool ke) din ko yaume-eid bana letey. aap ne puchha wo kon si aayat hai? usne jawab diya (sura Mayeda ki ye aayat ke) '' aaj maine tumharey Deen ko mukammal kar diya aur apni nemat tum par tamam kar di aur tumharey liye Deen Islam pasand kya.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ham us din aur us maqam ko) khub ( jantey hain jab ye aayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil hui (is waqt) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arafaat mein Juma ke din khade huey they.
46,"Najad walon mein aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, sar pareshan yani baal bikhrey huey they, ham uski awaz ki bhinbhinahat suntey they aur ham samajh nahi pa rahe they ke wo kya keh raha hai. yahan tak ke wo nazdeek aan pahuncha , jab malum hua ke wo Islam ke barey mein poochh raha hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Islam din raat mein panch namazein padhna hai, usne kaha bas iske siwa to aur koi Namaz mujh par nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi magar to nafl padhey (to aur baat hai) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhna. usne kaha aur to koi roza mujh par nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi magar to nafl rozey rakhey (to aur baat hai) Talha ne kaha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se zakat ka bayan kya. wo kehney laga ke bas aur koi sadqa mujh par nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi magar ye ke to nafl sadqa de (to aur baat hai) rawi ne kaha phir wo shakhs peeth mod kar chala . yun kehta jata tha, qism Allah ki main na us se badhaunga na ghataunga, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar ye sachcha hai to apni murad ko pahunch gaya."
47,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jo koi eman rakh kar aur sawab ki niyat se kisi musalman ke janazey ke sath jaey aur Namaz aur dafn se faraghat honey tak uske sath rahe to wo 2 qirat sawab lekar lautega har qirat itna bada hoga jaisey uhud ka pahad, aur jo shakhs janazey par Namaz padh kar dafn se pahley lot jaey to wo aik qirat sawab lekar lautega. Rooh ke sath us hadis ko Usman muazzan ne bhi riwayat kya hai. kaha ham se Auf ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se suna, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se agli riwayat ki tarah."
48,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalman ko gali deney se aadmi fasiq ho jata hai aur musalman se ladna kufr hai.
49,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hujre se nikley, logon ko shabe-qadr batana chahtey they (wo kon si raat hai) itney main 2 musalman aapas mein lad padey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, main to isliye bahar nikla tha ke tum ko shabe-qadr bataun aur falan-falan aadmi lad padey to wo mere dil se utha li gaee aur shayad usi mein kuchh tumhari behtri ho. (to ab aisa karo ke) shabe-qadr ko Ramazan ki sattaiswin , untiswin aur pachiswin raat mein talash karo."
50,aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon mein tashrif farma they ke aap ke paas aik shakhs aaya aur poochhney laga ke eman kisey kehtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke eman ye hai ke tum Allah paak ke wujood aur uski whdaniyat par eman lao aur uske farishton ke wujood par aur us ( Allah ( ki mulaqat ke bar-haq honey par aur uske rasulon ke bar-haq honey par aur marney ke baad dobara uthney par eman laao. phir usne puchha ke Islam kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir jawab diya ke Islam ye hai ke tum khalis Allah ki ibadat karo aur uske sath kisi ko Sharik na banao aur Namaz qaaim karo aur zakat farz ada karo aur Ramazan ke rozey rakho. phir usne ehsan ke mutaalliq poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ehsan ye hai ke tum Allah ki ibadat is tarah karo maano tum usey dekh rahe ho agar ye darja na hasil ho to phir ye to samjho ke wo tum ko dekh raha hai. phir us ne puchha ke qiyamat Kab aaeygi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iske barey mein jawab dene wala poochhney waley se kuchh zyada nahi janta (albatta) main tumhen uski nishaniyan batla sakta hun. wo ye hain ke jab londi apne aaqa ko janegi aur jab siyah oonton ke charaney waley (dehati log taraqqi kartey kartey) makanon ki tameer mein aik doosrey se bazi ley janey ki koshish karengey. (yaad rakho) qiyamat ka ilm un panch chizon mein hai jinko Allah ke siwa koi nahi janta. phir aap ne ye aayat padhi ke Allah hi ko qiyamat ka ilm hai ke wo Kab hogi (aakhir aayat tak) phir wo poochhney wala peeth pher kar janey laga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey wapas bula kar laao. log daud padey magar wo kahin nazar nahi aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo Jibraeel they jo logon ko unka Deen sikhaney aaey they. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (rh)) farmatey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un tamam baton ko eman hi qarar diya hai.
51,"Hiraql (Rome (mojooda Itly) ke baadshaah) ne unse kaha, maine tum se puchha tha ke us rasool ke manney waley badh rahe hain ya ghat rahe hain. tu ney jawab mein batlaya ke wo badh rahe hain. ( theek hai) eman ka yahi haal rehta hai yahan tak ke wo pura ho jaey aur maine tujh se puchha tha ke koi iske Deen mein aa kar phir usko bura jaan kar phir jata hai? tu ney kaha, nahi, aur eman ka yahi haal hai. jab uski khushi dil mein samaa jati hai to phir usko koi bura nahi samajh sakta."
52,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they halal khula hua hai aur haram bhi khula hua hai aur un donon ke darmyan kuchh cheezein shubeh ki hain jinko bahut log nahi jantey (ke halal hain ya haraam) phir jo koi shubeh ki chizon se bhi bach gaya usne apne Deen aur izzat ko bacha liya aur jo koi un shubeh ki chizon mein pad gaya uski misal us charwaahey ki hai jo (shaahi mahfooz) charaagaah ke aas-paas apne janwaron ko charaey. wo qareeb hai ke kabhi us charaagaah ke andar ghus jaey (aur shahi mujrim qarar paaey) sun lo har badshah ki aik charaagaah hoti hai. Allah ki charaagaah uski zameen par haram cheezein hain. (pas unse bacho aur) sun lo badan mein aik gosht ka tukda hai jab wo durust hoga Sara badan durust hoga aur jahan bigdaa Sara badan bigad gaya. sun lo wo tukda aadmi ka dil hai.
53,"main Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha karta tha wo mujh ko khas apne takht par bithatey (eik baar ( kehney lagey ke tum mere paas mustaqil taur par reh jao main apne maal mein se tumhara hissey muqarrar kar doonga . to main 2 maah tak unki khidmat mein reh gaya. phir kehney lagey ke abdul-Qais ka wafad jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to aap ne puchha ke ye kon si qaum ke log hain ya ye wafad kahan ka hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Rabee khandan ke log hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya marhaba us qaum ko ya us wafad ko na zaleel hone-waale na sharminda hone-waale (yani unka aana bahut khub hai ). wo kehney lagey aey Allah ke rasool! ham aap ki khidmat mein sirf un hurmat waley mahinon mein aa saktey hain kyonke hamarey aur aap ke darmyan Muzar ke kaafiron ka qabila abad hai. isliye aap ham ko aik aisi qatae baat batla dijiye jiski khabar ham apne pichhley logon ko bhi kar dein jo yahan nahi aaey aur is par amal-daramad karke ham jannat mein dakhil ho jayen aur unhon-ne aap se apne bartanon ke barey mein bhi poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko char baton ka hukm diya aur char qism ke bartanon ko istemal mein laney se mana farmaya, unko hukm diya ke aik akeley Allah par eman laao. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke jantey ho aik akeley Allah par eman laney ka matlab kya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool hi ko malum hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is baat ki gawahi dena ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske sachey rasool hain aur Namaz qaaim karna aur zakat ada karna aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhna aur maale-ghanimat se jo miley uska panchwan hissey (musalmanon ke baitul-maal mein) dakhil karna aur char bartanon ke istemal se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko mana farmaya, hare laakhii martban se aur kadu ke banaey huey bartan se, lakdi ke khode huey bartan se, aur roghni bartan se aur farmaya ke in baton ko hifz kar lo aur un logon ko bhi batla dena jo tum se peechhey hain aur yahan nahi aaey hain."
54,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya amal niyat hi se sahi hotey hain (ya niyat hi ke mutabiq unka badla milta hai) aur har aadmi ko wahi milega jo niyat karega . to jo koi Allah aur uske rasool ki raza ke liye hijrat karey uski hijrat Allah aur uske rasool ki taraf hogi aur jo koi duniya kamaane ke liye ya kisi aurat se shadi karne ke liye hijrat karega to uski hijrat unhi kaamon ke liye hogi.
55,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab aadmi sawab ki niyat se apne ahal w ayaal par kharch karey to wo bhi uske liye sadqa hai.
56,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya beshak to jo kuchh kharch karey aur us se teri niyat Allah ki raza hasil karni ho to tujh ko iska sawab milega. yahan tak ke is par bhi jo to apni biwi ke munh mein daley.
57,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine Namaz qaaim karne aur zakat ada karne aur har musalman ki khair khahi karne par bait ki.
58,"jis din Mughira-bin-Shoba ( Hakim Kufa (ka intiqal hua to wo khutbe ke liye khadey huey aur Allah ki tareef aur khoobi bayan ki aur kaha tum ko akeley Allah ka dar rakhna chahiye uska koi Sharik nahi aur tahammul aur itminan se rehna chahiye us waqt tak ke koi doosra Hakim tumharey uper aaey aur wo abhi aaney wala hai. phir farmaya ke apne marney waley Hakim ke liye duaaey maghfirat karo kyonke wo ( Mughira ( bhi maafi ko pasand karta tha phir kaha ke iske baad tum ko malum hona chahiye ke main aik baar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur maine arz kya ke main aap se Islam par bait karta hun Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se har musalman ki khair-khahi ke liye shart ki, to maine us shart par aap se bait kar li ( to (us masjid ke rab ki qism ke main tumhara khair-khaah hun phir istighfar kya aur member se utar aaey."
